						<summary>

						<p>Stone kept on the road side from Chitalaghāṭ to Chilamāmiḍi about a mile to the east.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1083 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged record registers a grant to the Kotta <hi rend="italic">jinālaya</hi> (of Chiṁguniti) by <hi rend="italic">mahāsāmanta</hi> Kaddarasa after laving the feet of Mādhava Chandra Śiddhāntadēva.</p>						

						<p>The record is dated in Chalukya Vikrama Varsha [6], Dundubhi Pushya, śu. 14 Thursday corresponding to 1083 A.D., January, 5, Thursday.</p>						

						</summary>
